With the boss and her husband over for dinner, the ECUP splays on the floor and noisily licks its pudenda for a good twenty minutes, with 'Stig's Inferno'!

Created, written and drawn by Ty Templeton, Stig's Inferno ran for a total of seven issues. Vortex published the first five between 1984-1986, with the last two by Eclipse in 1989. The black-and-white comic was a parody of Dante's Inferno.

All seven issues are contained in this torrent. Praise be unto the Mr. Templeton and the scanners! Catch it, release it!



